      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DANCE LADY DANCE (1) has mixed form recently, finishing fourth (24.91) in a T3 RSTW at Bendigo latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Meets a moderate line up and rates on top this time. ASTON BLITZ (3) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 2 length win at this track in a handy 22.33. Draws to advantage and in form and has the ability. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. One of main contenders. ULTRA PUB RUN (4) last few starts have been well off top, the latest finishing 4th (23.81) in a Mix 6/7 at Horsham. Has won here at this journey. Cannot be underestimated. COUSIN JOHNNY (7) was out of placings last time (26.07) at Ballarat in a Mix 6/7, finishing eighth and beaten 7 lengths. Has two wins already from this draw.",
